name: Best Dining
tag_list: local, restaurant, dining, social, facebook, search, consumer, reviews
overview: BestDining.com is a premier resource for dining information, unbiased reviews, ratings and live updated restaurant photos. The home page serves as local restaurant portal tracking userâ€™s location and then displaying the best local dining options available in each major cuisine type. Users can use the search engine through searching a cuisine type and location or click through the directory to explore top restaurants per cuisine type in each major city nationwide. In short BestDining.com is the ultimate resource for dining enthusiasts and food lovers alike who want to explore the best new restaurants and global cuisines in their local area. BestDining.com is yet another of many that have joined forces with Facebook through their Facebook Connect platform with allows Facebook users to login and leave reviews on their favorite restaurants. Additionally Facebook users can add the BestDining Facebook Application to their profile which highlights their personal reviews and favorite local restaurant recommendations.
